blast
Class NCBIBlastPutCommand

java.lang.Object
  filters.NCBIBlastPutCommand

public class NCBIBlastPutCommand
extends java.lang.Object

This class specifies the parameters for a blast "put" command directed using the BLAST API. The only required parameter is a nucleotide or protein sequence.
